Cinema HD is an online media file search engine and browser. It acts as a client-side web crawler to crawl and scrape publicly available content and hyperlinks on the internet. This app is purely for educational and personal use. All media files, hyperlinks, and content should be deleted within 24 hours after being saved.\10\10Cinema HD functions just like any other search engine, such as Google. Cinema HD does not host, upload, or manage any videos, films, or content on its servers. It simply crawls, aggregates, and displays links in a convenient, user-friendly interface. Cinema HD has no control over what content is made available online/offline. It merely scrapes 3rd-party websites that are publicly accessible via any regular web browser. Hence, Cinema HD app is not responsible for the copyright, legality, accuracy, compliance, decency, or any other aspect of the content displayed. It is the responsibility of the user to avoid any actions that might violate the laws governing their locality.\10\10Any legal issues regarding the content on this application should be taken up with the actual file hosts and providers themselves as we are not affiliated with them. \10\10In case of copyright infringement, please directly contact the responsible parties or the streaming websites.\10\10Cinema HD strongly believes in the protection of intellectual property and would be willing to assist when possible and applicable. All content is accessed directly from the third-party services. All other trademarks, logos, and images are the property of their respective and rightful owners. \10\10Cinema HD has no control over what media is put up or taken down. It merely scrapes 3rd-party websites that are publicly accessible via any regular web browser. It is the responsibility of the user to avoid any actions that might violate the laws governing their locality. Use Cinema HD at your own risk.
